msgstr "直線"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../user_manual/snapping.rst:61
msgid "Rectangle"
msgstr "多角形"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../user_manual/snapping.rst:62
msgid "Ellipse"
msgstr "三日月"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../user_manual/snapping.rst:63
msgid "Polyline"
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../user_manual/snapping.rst:64
msgid "Path"
msgstr "パス"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../user_manual/snapping.rst:65
msgid "Freehand path"
msgstr "フリーハンドパス"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../user_manual/snapping.rst:66
msgid "Polygon"
msgstr "ポリゴン"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../user_manual/snapping.rst:67
msgid "Gradient"
msgstr "グラデーション"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../user_manual/snapping.rst:68
msgid "Shape Handling tool"
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../user_manual/snapping.rst:69
msgid "The Text-tool"
msgstr "テキストツール"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../user_manual/snapping.rst:70
msgid "Assistant editing tools"
msgstr "アシスト編集ツール"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../user_manual/snapping.rst:71
msgid ""
"The move tool (note that it snaps to the cursor position and not the "
"bounding box of the layer, selection or whatever you are trying to move)"
msgstr ""
"移動ツール (レイヤーのバウンディングボックス、選択や他の物ではなく、カーソル"
"の位置にスナップすることに留意してください。)"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../user_manual/snapping.rst:72
msgid "The Transform tool"
msgstr "変形ツール"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../user_manual/snapping.rst:73
msgid "Rectangle select"
msgstr "多角形選択"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../user_manual/snapping.rst:74
msgid "Elliptical select"
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../user_manual/snapping.rst:75
msgid "Polygonal select"
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../user_manual/snapping.rst:76
msgid "Path select"
msgstr "パス選択"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../user_manual/snapping.rst:77
msgid "Guides themselves can be snapped to grids and vectors"
msgstr "ガイド自身はグリッドやベクターにスナップできます。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../user_manual/snapping.rst:79
msgid ""
"Snapping doesn’t have a sensitivity yet, and by default is set to 10 screen "
"pixels."
msgstr "スナップにはまだ感度はなく、既定で画面10ピクセル分に設定されています。"

